name: Honours Thesis
description: This course is designed to give students experience in the design and execution of an independent senior thesis under the supervision of a faculty member. In order to register in the course, students must complete and submit an application form to the Department of Geography by March 31 of the preceding year. This course may fulfill field day components. Please consult with your supervisor.
prerequisites: Completion of 3rd-year requirements for the Specialist program in GGR Arts and Science.
